    "htmlObj": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22grid-content%20%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22grid-column%20%20%20%20%22%20style%3D%22width%3A%20100%25%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20padding-left%3A0px%3Bpadding-right%3A0px%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20background-image%3A%20none%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20background-size%3A%20cover%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20background-repeat%3A%20no-repeat%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20background-position%3A%20center%20center%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20top%3A%200px%3B%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%22%3E%0A%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22widget-row%20%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22widget%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20widgetResponsive%20textWidget%20col19%22%20id%3D%22text-widget-1714643030626%22%20data-type%3D%22TextWidget%22%20data-delay%3D%22%22%20data-animation-duration%3D%22%22%20data-animation-delay%3D%22%22%20data-animation%3D%22lazyAnimation-%22%20style%3D%22margin-top%3A%200px%3B%20margin-left%3A%200px%3B%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22text-widget-content%22%3E%3Cp%3E%u201CAs%20a%20kid%2C%20I%20loved%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi.%20Welcoming%20Ganpati%20ji%2C%20celebrating%20his%20arrival%2C%20attending%20Ganpati%20decoration%20competitions%20%u2013%20these%20are%20my%20favourite%20memories%20from%20my%20childhood.%20For%20me%2C%20going%20to%20different%20pandals%20and%20seeing%20different%20kinds%20of%20Ganesh%20idols%20was%20very%20exciting%21%20But%20as%20much%20as%20I%20loved%20the%20festival%2C%20seeing%20how%20our%20celebrations%20disturbed%20nature%20saddened%20me.%20Since%20my%20parents%20were%20environmentalists%2C%20they%u2019d%20tell%20me%20about%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20POP%2C%20and%20that%20stayed%20with%20me.%20They%20taught%20me%2C%20%u2018You%20should%20always%20protect%20nature.%u2019%20Thus%2C%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%20being%20environmentally%20conscious%20was%20instilled%20in%20me.%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EThat%u2019s%20why%2C%208%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20started%20getting%20a%20Ganesh%20idol%20to%20my%20office%2C%20it%20was%20obvious%20that%20I%u2019d%20go%20for%20an%20eco-friendly%20option.%20Initially%2C%20I%u2019d%20get%20a%20plant%20idol.%20But%20one%20day%2C%20while%20randomly%20scrolling%20through%20social%20media%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20picture%20posted%20by%20a%20man%20from%20Pune%20%u2013%20that%20of%20an%20alum%20stone%20on%20which%20there%20was%20a%20carving%20of%20Ganesh.%20That%u2019s%20when%20the%20seed%20was%20planted%u2026%20I%20wondered%2C%20%u2018Can%20we%20make%20idols%20using%20alum%3F%u2019%20Since%20alum%20is%20commonly%20used%20for%20purification%20of%20water%2C%20I%20thought%20it%u2019d%20be%20great%20if%20idols%20made%20using%20alum%20would%20be%20immersed%20in%20water.%20They%u2019d%20purify%20the%20water%20body%20they%u2019d%20be%20immersed%20in%2C%20thus%20reversing%20some%20of%20the%20pollution%20we%20cause%21%20So%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20friends%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20local%20idol%20makers%20with%20this%20idea.%20But%20most%20weren%u2019t%20keen%20on%20it%20because%20making%20those%20idols%20required%20extra%20effort.%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%20%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20takers%20for%20my%20idea%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20matters%20into%20my%20own%20hands.%20I%20thought%2C%20%u2018Why%20not%20try%20making%20this%20on%20my%20own%3F%u2019%20After%20all%2C%20I%20had%20the%20idea%20and%20the%20right%20motivation.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20wasn%u2019t%20about%20business%20%u2013%20it%20was%20my%20way%20of%20serving%20the%20environment.%20So%2C%20I%20started%20thinking%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20making%20alum%20idols%20on%20my%20own%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20few%20engineer%20friends.%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20first%20step%2C%20I%20researched%20intensively%20about%20alum%2C%20its%20types%20and%20how%20to%20give%20it%20shape%2C%20etc.%20Initially%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20use%20a%20huge%202ft%20alum%20stone%20in%2020ltr%20muddy%20water%20just%20to%20see%20if%20it%20would%20be%20able%20to%20purify%20that%20much%20water%2C%20and%20it%20actually%20did%21%20This%20strengthened%20my%20motive%20even%20further%21%20So%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20my%20friends%2CI%20made%20makeshift%20idols%20that%20were%202ft%20slabs%20of%20alum%20stone%20with%20Ganesh%20ji%20painted%20on%20it.%20However%2C%20since%20they%20weren%u2019t%20very%20pleasing%20to%20look%20at%2C%20we%20didn%u2019t%20find%20many%20takers.%20This%20pushed%20us%20to%20improvise%20and%20make%20better-looking%20idols.%20After%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20research%2C%20our%20prototype%20idol%20was%20finally%20ready%20in%202018%21%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%20%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feeling%20of%20seeing%20your%20idea%20come%20to%20life%20is%20incomparable%u2026%20I%20felt%20proud%20of%20what%20I%20had%20built.%20Years%20of%20research%20had%20finally%20yielded%20into%20the%20results%20I%20had%20set%20out%20to%20accomplish.%20Being%20an%20engineer%2C%20I%20was%20now%20able%20to%20make%20an%20idol%20-%20and%20this%20proved%20the%20%u2018Engineers%20can%20do%20anything%u2019%20saying%20true%21%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%20%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20was%20of%20course%20proud%20of%20my%20innovation%2C%20but%20what%20came%20as%20a%20pleasant%20surprise%20was%20strangers%20noticing%20my%20work.%20They%20noticed%20that%20I%20was%20genuinely%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20and%20make%20the%20festival%20a%20bit%20more%20eco-friendly%2C%20and%20they%20enthusiastically%20supported%20me.%20I%20never%20advertised%20my%20creation%2C%20but%20word-of-mouth%20helped%20my%20idols%20get%20noticed.%20Even%20kids%20near%20our%20production%20unit%20noticed%20our%20work%20and%20encouraged%20their%20families%20to%20adopt%20these%20idols.%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%20%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%204%20years%20later%2C%20I%u2019ve%20sold%20around%203000%20idols%20across%20the%20country.%20I%20know%20it%u2019s%20a%20small%20number%2C%20but%20every%20drop%20makes%20an%20ocean%20and%20I%u2019m%20happy%20that%20I%u2019m%20able%20to%20make%20a%20small%20impact%20with%20my%20innovation%21%20I%u2019ve%20realised%20that%20people%20want%20to%20save%20the%20environment%20but%20they%20don%u2019t%20have%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20do%20it%20%u2013%20my%20motive%20is%20to%20make%20these%20alum%20idols%20a%20tiny%20way%20for%20them%20to%20help.%20Also%2C%20what%20makes%20me%20happier%20is%20that%20people%20who%20buy%20my%20idols%20once%20end%20up%20placing%20orders%20every%20year%2C%20thus%20doing%20their%20bit%20for%20the%20environment%21%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%20%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20people%20approach%20me%20saying%20they%20want%20to%20felicitate%20me%2C%20but%20honestly%20I%20don%u2019t%20want%20that%u2026%20This%20is%20not%20a%20business%20for%20me%20%u2013%20it%u2019s%20just%20my%20passion%20for%20the%20environment%21%20I%20am%20more%20than%20willing%20to%20guide%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20make%20these%20alum%20idols%20-%20even%20if%20a%20few%20people%20take%20up%20this%20initiative%2C%20we%20can%20collectively%20bring%20about%20a%20positive%20change.%20Today%2C%20people%20know%20me%20as%20%u2018Vishal%20alum%20idols%20wala%u2019%20and%20that%u2019s%20all%20the%20recognition%20I%20need%21%3C/p%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C/div%3E%0A%20%20%3C/div%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C/div%3E%3C/div%3E"
