    "title": "Neha – The Smile That Greets You at 6 AM",
    "content": "From greeting early guests to calming cranky travelers, Neha’s smile never fades...",
    "image": "https://content.app-sources.com/s/810084476556330001/uploads/Downloaded/Website2-4064083.jpg?format=webp",
    "htmlObj": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22text-widget-content%22%3E%3Cp%3E%u201CIf%20there%u2019s%20one%20thing%20that%20has%20excited%20me%20the%20most%20as%20a%20kid%2C%20it%20was%20planes%21%20Whenever%20I%u2019d%20see%20them%2C%20flying%20high%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20I%u2019d%20be%20in%20awe%21%20I%20was%208%20when%20I%20first%20sat%20in%20one%2C%20after%20we%20landed%2C%20I%20told%20Papa%2C%20%u2018One%20day%2C%20I%u2019ll%20be%20a%20pilot%21%u2019%20He%20just%20smiled%20at%20me%20and%20ruffled%20my%20hair.%20I%20think%20he%20didn%u2019t%20take%20me%20seriously%20then.%20But%20I%20had%20decided%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20the%20air%20force.%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%20%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20after%20my%2012th%2C%20I%20went%20back%20to%20Papa%20and%20repeated%2C%20%u2018I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20pilot.%u2019%20This%20time%2C%20he%20paid%20attention%20to%20me.%20He%20asked%20me%2C%20%u2018Are%20you%20sure%3F%u2019%20When%20I%20nodded%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%u2018Go%20for%20it%2C%20beta.%20The%20sky%27s%20the%20limit%21%u2019%20We%20took%20a%20loan%20and%20finally%2C%20my%20training%20began.%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E2%20years%20of%20putting%20my%20heart%20and%20soul%20in%20my%20training%20later%2C%20I%20finally%20got%20my%20pilot%20license.%20My%20dreams%20had%20gotten%20wings%2C%20I%20was%20ecstatic%21%20Soon%20after%2C%20I%20landed%20a%20job%20with%20Air%20India%2C%20the%20national%20carrier.%20I%20still%20remember%20my%20first%20flight%u2013it%20was%20from%20Bombay%20to%20Delhi%3B%20I%20was%20so%20nervous.%20But%20the%20moment%20I%20sat%20in%20the%20cockpit%2C%20I%20felt%20at%20home%20and%20flew%20confidently.%20Papa%20was%20so%20happy%21%20Whenever%20any%20relative%20asked%2C%20%u2018How%20will%20she%20settle%20now%3F%u2019%20He%u2019d%20reply%2C%20%u2018Meri%20beti%20udne%20ke%20liye%20bani%20hai%21%u2019%20He%u2019d%20hype%20so%20much%20in%20front%20of%20others%2C%20especially%20after%20I%20became%20one%20of%20the%20first%20few%20women%20pilots%20for%20Boeing%20777.%20Papa%20was%20on%20cloud%20nine%21%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20loved%20my%20job%u2013I%20loved%20watching%20terrains%20change%20from%20up%20above.%20But%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20more%20than%20just%20travel.%20And%20so%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%20and%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20rescue%20mission%20came%20into%20being%2C%20I%20volunteered%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it%21%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20Maa%20and%20Papa%20were%20worried.%20But%20when%20I%20explained%20how%20important%20the%20mission%20was%2C%20they%20reluctantly%20agreed.%20My%20first%20rescue%20flight%20was%20to%20Shanghai.%20Our%20aim%20was%20to%20bring%20back%20all%20the%20Indians%20stuck%20there.%20I%20will%20never%20forget%20that%20flight%20%u2013%20while%20going%20to%20Shanghai%20there%20was%20tension.%20China%20being%20the%20hot%20spot%20of%20Covid%2C%20everyone%20was%20distressed.%20We%20all%20wore%20hazmat%20suits%20through%20the%20course%20of%20the%20flight%2C%20I%20flew%20it%20wearing%20one.%20Even%20when%20we%20onboarded%20people%2C%20we%20were%20being%20extra%20cautious.%20When%20we%20finally%20landed%20in%20India%2C%20the%20passengers%20gave%20us%20a%20standing%20ovation.%20One%20little%20girl%20came%20up%20to%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%u2018I%20want%20to%20be%20like%20you%21%u2019%20And%20I%20told%20her%20what%20Papa%20told%20me%2C%20%u2018The%20sky%27s%20the%20limit%21%u2019%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20I%20did%203%20rescue%20missions%20in%20a%20month.%20The%20flights%20were%20long%20and%20wearing%20hazmat%20suits%20made%20it%20tough%2C%20but%20I%20had%20a%20responsibility%20towards%20all%20those%20Indians%20who%20were%20stuck.%20They%20kept%20me%20going.%20Once%2C%20I%20even%20flew%20to%20bring%20medical%20aid%20to%20India.%20That%20was%20the%20strangest%20flight%20%u2013%20instead%20of%20passengers%2C%20we%20travelled%20with%20hundreds%20of%20carton%20boxes.%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%201st%20year%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20are%20in%20the%203rd%20year%20today%20%u2013%20Mission%20Vande%20Bharat%20is%20still%20pretty%20active.%20In%20fact%2C%20tomorrow%20I%u2019m%20flying%20out%20to%20Newark%20to%20bring%20those%20stranded%20back.%20Papa%20says%20he%20is%20proud%20of%20me.%20He%20recently%20told%20me%2C%20%u2018I%20used%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20sky%27s%20the%20limit.%20But%20you%u2019ve%20scaled%20even%20that%21%20Keep%20flying%21%u2019%20And%20that%u2019s%20what%20I%u2019m%20going%20to%20do%u2026%20Keep%20flying%21%3C/p%3E%3C/div%3E"
  }
]
